sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant PasswordUtils
participant DB
participant JWT

User->>Frontend: Submit login form
Frontend->>API: POST /api/auth/login
API->>API: authRateLimit
alt Rate limited
API-->>Frontend: 429 Too many requests
Frontend-->>User: Show rate limit message
else Allowed
API->>API: Validate email and password
alt Missing email or password
API-->>Frontend: 400 Email and password are required
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Provided
API->>DB: Query employee by email (primary schema)
alt Primary query error
alt ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR
DB-->>API: error code ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR
API->>DB: Query employee by email (legacy schema)
alt Fallback error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
else Fallback success
DB-->>API: rows
end
else Other DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
end
else Primary query success
DB-->>API: rows
end
API->>API: Check if employee exists
alt No employee
API-->>Frontend: 401 Invalid credentials
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Employee found
API->>PasswordUtils: verifyPassword(stored, provided)
alt Password mismatch
PasswordUtils-->>API: matched = false
API-->>Frontend: 401 Invalid credentials
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Password match
alt Legacy password
PasswordUtils-->>API: legacy = true
API->>PasswordUtils: hashPassword(provided)
API->>DB: Update password + reset flag (fallback on ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR)
else Not legacy
API->>DB: Update last_login_at (ignore ER_BAD_FIELD_ERROR)
end
API->>JWT: sign token
API->>API: set auth cookie
API-->>Frontend: 200 Login successful + employee
Frontend-->>User: Signed in
end
end
end
end
